{
  "texts": [
    "Such a condition would be ideally met between pauses in speech or at the end of a sentence.",
    "The Whisper ASR model (Radford et al., 2022) interacts with the VAD segmenter by receiving the segmented audio inputs.",
    "The Whisper portion of the Segmented ASR Pipeline is designed to have Whisper transcribe the audio input using a stable transcription policy, leveraging a context mechanism.",
    "The stable transcription policy followed aims to create consistent, accurate transcriptions.",
    "It works by committing a transcription to a stable transcription buffer once it repeats a transcription for a given audio interval."
  ]
}